  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Here are two samples I've made:\r\n- [reproducing the original issue](http://workable-camera.surge.sh/)\r\n- [with the issue fixed](http://cut-song.surge.sh/)\r\n\r\nIn order to fix the issue, you need to only use a single value for the filter and use the string form of the value like so:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar search = instantsearch({\r\n  // Replace with your own values\r\n  appId: 'JTH1JDTDFT',\r\n  apiKey: '1d8e2d4aa2a19623ee5fc10fb0d85f83', // search only API key, no ADMIN key\r\n  indexName: 'test-is-toggle',\r\n  searchParameters: {\r\n    disjunctiveFacetsRefinements: {\r\n      \"is-popular\": [\"true\"],\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n});\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2018-05-22T13:11:09Z",
